    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        I am a passionate and results-oriented digital marketer with a proven track record of developing and executing successful online marketing campaigns. With a deep understanding of the digital landscape, I am skilled in leveraging various digital channels to drive brand awareness,
increase website traffic, and generate leads.. I hope you find
        it useful!
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://twitter.com/manuelernestog" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/manuelernestog/astrofy" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">
